data.description: **ASSUMABLE VA LOAN AT 2.75% INTEREST RATE**HOUSE IS NOT ''ON'' ORANGE GROVE AND IS SET BACK FROM ROAD**DISTRICT 16 SCHOOLS**RVs/RENTALS ALLOWEDSituated at the top of a cul-de-sac, among the saguaro studded Catalina Foothills, this stunning 4 Bedroom/2Bath Burnt Adobe Territorial brings the majestic Catalina Mountains into view from your sparkling salt water pool. This updated property reflects the warmth and charm of the southwest, with modern amenities to support the function of today's lifestyle. For the aspiring chef, the kitchen is equipped with not one, but two ovens, PLUS a convection oven. Kitchen features: ample cabinetry, crown molding, gorgeous granite counters, pantry, breakfast bar, Samsung stainless steel appliances and tile backsplash, adding an elegant touch!
